  "title": "Project Manager ( Electrical)",
  "description": "<ul>\n  <li>Lead and manage electrical projects from planning to completion.</li>\n  <li>Supervise and guide the project and site teams.</li>\n  <li>Review designs, drawings, and technical specifications.</li>\n  <li>Manage project budgets, schedules, and resources efficiently.</li>\n  <li>Coordinate with clients, consultants, and contractors.</li>\n  <li>Ensure compliance with quality, safety, and regulatory standards.</li>\n  <li>Oversee testing, commissioning, and project handover.</li>\n  <li>Prepare progress reports and resolve project issues promptly.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be contacted. All applications will be handled confidentially. By submitting your application, you agree to the collection, use, retention, and disclosure of your personal information to prospective employers.</p>\n<p>EA License No: 20C0270</p>\n<p>EA Personnel No: R22110980</p>\n<p>EA Personnel Name: Lim Hooi Mei</p>",
